{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 69,
  "title": "第六十九章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "用兵有言﹕「吾不敢為主而為客，不敢進寸而退尺。」是謂行無行，"
    },
    {
      "text": "攘無臂，扔無敵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "執無兵。禍莫大於輕敵，輕敵幾喪吾寶。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故抗兵相加，哀者勝矣。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼遂不止。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "行，謂行陳也，言以謙退哀慈，不敢為物先，用戰猶行無行，攘無臂，執無兵，扔無敵也，言無有與之抗也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言吾哀慈謙退，非欲以取强，無敵於天下也。不得已而卒至於無敵，斯乃吾之所以為大禍也。寶，三寶也，故曰，幾亡吾寶。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "抗，舉也；加，當也。哀者，必相惜而不趣利避害，故必勝。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
